source.name: Sun et al., Median Group via Epoch (2022)
source.dataPublishedBy: Hobbhahn and Besiroglu (2022), "Trends in GPU price-performance". Published online at epochai.org. Retrieved from: 'https://epochai.org/blog/trends-in-gpu-price-performance' [online resource]
source.additionalInfo: This dataset by the research group Epoch collates two existing datasets on GPU price-performance: • Median Group (2019). Feasibility of Training an AGI using Deep RL: A Very Rough Estimate. • Sun et al. (2019). Summarizing CPU and GPU Design Trends with Product Data. arXiv. The report by Epoch researchers Hobbhahn & Besiroglu (2022) describes their collation method, as well as their findings from statistically analyzing the trends in GPU price-performance.
